---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Chronosphere">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-8">About Chronosphere</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="mb-6">
          Welcome to Chronosphere, your gateway to exploring the fascinating world of history. Founded by a passionate historian and developer, our mission is to make historical knowledge accessible and engaging for everyone.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          At Chronosphere, we believe that understanding history is crucial for comprehending our present and shaping our future. Our goal is to present historical content in an engaging, accurate, and thought-provoking manner.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
          <li>In-depth articles about significant historical events</li>
          <li>Profiles of influential historical figures</li>
          <li>Analysis of historical trends and their impact on modern society</li>
          <li>Regular updates with new historical content</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Join Our Journey</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you're a history enthusiast, student, or simply curious about the past, we invite you to join us on this fascinating journey through time. Together, let's explore the stories that have shaped our world.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>